metadata.name: Dopplez #1
metadata.description: The Dopplez NFT is a PFP and is set to provide user-satisfying quality. We also want to instill Dopplez's own characteristics in the NFT collection, such as the various properties, colors and representations of Dopplez NFTs, and 1of1. Dopplez is a 7777 PFP NFT stored in Ethereum blockchain and IPFS high-quality metadata, a means to claim ownership of those who will be friends with Dopplez.
